{"tid":927450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"萬寶路母公司 Altria傳洽購大麻生產商Cronos","createTime":"2018-12-04T07:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T07:22:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be4ba4457e06f78158b782f6e20e09460bf4a9b4","tid":927450,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"《金融時報》引述消息人士報道，萬寶路生產商Altria 就收購加拿大大麻生產商Cronos 展開早期談判，有可能成為大型煙草商對大麻公司的首宗重磅收購。<br />\n受消息刺激，Cronos隔夜股價上漲14%至10.39美元，令公司市值達到19億美元。<br />\n自加拿大１０月通過大麻合法化後，包括加利福尼亞州在內的美國多個州份同樣進行類似的法例修改，令大麻行業吸引投資者的注意。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN281204250&amp;category=macro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fnewsid%3DETN281204250%26category%3Dmacro&d=AtWwe%2FdLOZlZPdCPsK%2F9a26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7392784e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?newsid=ETN281204250&amp;category=macro</a><br />\n<br />\nAltria好有錢又買JUUL又買大麻生產商<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}